      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S MAYHEM (8) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (29.93) at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Capable of going well again. FLAMIN' JOE (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (30.21) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has good early burn and is drawn to be prominent. Has ability and can atone. CONDO BANDIT (1) turned in a solid run last start over 350m at Goulburn finishing 4th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (19.98). Won at her only start from this box. Can figure in the finish. MABEL'S WAY (2) cannot be written off despite a miss here at her latest outing.",
